<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-02-0776 </DOCNO><TEXT>Computing Services Writing and Editing Standards explains how to writeand organize technical information clearly and concisely; it also establishesArgonne National Laboratory Computing Services standards for grammar,usage, style, formats, and publication procedures. This manual will enablewriters to produce better documents consistent with Computing Servicesstandards in less time. Applying the specified principles will also speedup the editing, review, and revision processes.</TEXT></DOC>